						               													<description>Kappa is a mercenary ronin for Ninja All-Stars. Ronin bring potent new abilities to a player&amp;rsquo;s team that are entirely unique to them. As mercenaries, ronin may be used by any player, on any team. This makes ronin invaluable assets for every team, regardless of clan, since they may be used to supplement a team&amp;rsquo;s weaknesses in battle or further augment their strengths.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The Kappa are wild, dangerous kami who inhabit Kagejima&amp;rsquo;s lakes, rivers, and swamps. Wily and withdrawn by nature, they can be found overturning boats and drowning unwary children. Despite this, several clans have successfully coaxed these exceptionally strong and stealthy creatures into performing services&amp;hellip;often with the sacrifice of food, livestock, or even the village elder&amp;rsquo;s firstborn child.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Highlights:&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Introduces Unique Abilities&amp;#10;    Water, Earth, and Void Affinities&amp;#10;    Fully Assembled Model&amp;#10;    Wild and Wily Kami Ronin&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
